    <text id="F1104T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Freedley tells Hiester of the army's movement and predicts an imminent clash with
                    Confederates. He mentions the isolation of soldiers from news and their
                    immersion in rumors; and he wishes that he could visit Hiester.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
            

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1863-06-18">June 18<hi rend="super">
                                <hi rend="underline">th</hi>
                        </hi> 1863</date>
                        <name type="place">Camp <unclear>5</unclear>
                            <abbr expan="Infantry">Infty</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Maria</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have taken this opportunity to write you a line I ascertained yesterday that my
                    last two dispatches were intercepted at Army <orig reg="Headquarters">Head
                        Quarters</orig>. We are now near Leesburg after the rebel army. I expect we
                    will soon have another engagement. I do not know the news and we hear a variety
                    of rumors. I have not seen a paper for a week and intercourse is entirely
                    stopped. Our letters do not reach their <del hand="h1">
                        <unclear>informal</unclear>
                    </del> destination I hope you have left <unclear>Millmont</unclear> and that you
                    are not exposed to the rudeness of the soldiers. I am so sorry that I could not
                    take advantage of my "leave" to see you before their "raid" for I do not know
                    when I will be able to come now. I will now endeavor to obtain a <abbr
                        expan="Pennsylvania">Penna</abbr> regiment I'm so sorry that I could not
                        <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> to these <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> to defend the promotion.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Ever Your Friend</salute>
                    <signed>HWFreedley</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">P.S. I wrote to your father at the Continental
                    Hotel</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
